image:Beppu-station.jpg 250px thumb Beppu Station
nihongo Beppu Station  Beppu-eki is the main railway station for the city of Beppu in ita Prefecture, Japan, which is famous for its onsen. It is situated on the Nipp Main Line. The station, and all trains serving it, are operated by JR Kysh.
Limited Express Trains
 Sonic train Sonic Hakata Station Hakata - ita Station ita
 Nichirin Hakata - Miyazaki Station Miyazaki
 Yufuin-no-mori Yufuin-no-mori, Yufu Hakata - Beppu
 Trans-Kyushu Limited Express Beppu - Hitoyoshi Station Hitoyoshi
Layout
There is two side platforms and four island platforms. 
